Embeddings vs Keywords

| Keyword Search                      | Embedding Search                 |
| ----------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Looks for exact words               | Understands meaning              |
| Misses synonyms                     | Finds related concepts           |
| Simple text matching                | Semantic search                  |
| Less effective for natural language | Better for conversational search |


=====

Embedding vs Vector

| Embedding                                                                        | Vector                              |
| -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| The process/output of converting data into a meaningful numerical representation | The numerical array itself          |
| Focuses on preserving semantic meaning                                           | General mathematical representation |


